    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>University of Cologne</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this trial is

        1. to determine the recommended dose of everolimus for a subsequent Phase II trial

        2. to determine the efficacy of everolimus plus DHAP
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
